close_reason: Starter extension health warning fixed; linked pm test passed and patched temp install health is clean.
body: "Dogfood finding: installing docs/examples/starter-extension in a clean temp project worked, but pm health --check-only returned ok=false because the sample no-op migration was reported as pending. This makes the reference SDK extension look unhealthy immediately after install."
